companyInfo.introduction: Cng ty C phn FPT (FPT) c thnh lp nm 1988 t cng ty cng ngh thc phm thuc Vin nghin cu cng ngh quc gia. FPT l tp on cng ngh hng u ti Vit Nam, hot ng trong cng ngh, vin thng v gio dc. Vi hn 100 gii php phn mm v mng li vin thng ph sng ton quc, FPT p ng nhu cu a dng ca ngnh cng nghip. Tp on cng u t vo gio dc v c hai trng i hc: i hc FPT v i hc Trc tuyn FUNiX. FPT nim yt trn S Giao dch Chng khon TP.HCM t 2006, th hin s n nh v tng trng bn vng. Vi cam kt cht lng v s i mi, FPT ng gp vo s pht trin ca ngnh cng nghip cng ngh v xy dng mi quan h i tc lu di, mang li gi tr cho khch hng v cng ng.
